SEC. 2. The sale of said parcel of land shall be subject to the following conditions which shall be embodied in the contract of sale:

That the Philippine National Red Cross shall not transfer the parcel of land without the previous authorization by the President of the Philippines nor encumber the same except to government-owned or controlled corporations ;

That the land shall not be used for any purpose or activity other than that to which it is orginally intended;

That violation of any of these conditions shall automatically revert the land to the National Government.

SEC. 3. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Enacted into law without executive signature on June 21, 1969.
